data.description: Exquisite contemporary home that exudes beauty & elegance, offering awe-inspiring 180-degree western exposure views of the Olympics, Puget Sound & Narrows Bridge. Enjoy breathtaking sunsets from every rm as the large windows stretch across, framing the landscape for a full view of nature's artistry. The main flr has been tastefully remodeled, creating a seamless blend of modern style & comfort. You'll find a primary suite that leaves no detail untouched, a spa-like ensuite, cozy sitting area & a fireplace. The lower level of this home is designed for fantastic entertaining, complete with a built-in bar area & 3 bdrms. On any typical NW day, you take can advantage of the indoor atrium pool, hot tub w/2 changing rms. Lifestyle of tranquility.
